{"title":"如今天旱心不慌","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":3,"day":31}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今天旱心不慌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前天旱心发慌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又叩头来又烧香；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祷告老天天不灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田中禾苗旱死光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼人，流离失所苦难当！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今天旱心不慌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员就是活龙王；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千渠万井吐清水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田中禾苗翻碧浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员们，高歌万曲赞颂党！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}